headline.main: High Soviet Aide Confirms Spacewoman's Pregnancy

results.snippet: MOSCOW, Jan., 29 -- Reports that Capt. Valentina V. Tereshkova, the Soviet spacewoman, was expecting a child have been confirmed by a high-ranking Soviet official.

byline.original: Special to The New York Times

results.lead_paragraph: MOSCOW, Jan., 29 -- Reports that Capt. Valentina V. Tereshkova, the Soviet spacewoman, was expecting a child have been confirmed by a high-ranking Soviet official.
